<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Punto" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Punto,</orth> a thrust or stroke in fencing: <cit><quote>to see thee pass thy p.</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.3.26" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 3, 26</bibl></cit>. <emph>the p. reverso</emph> == a backhanded stroke or cut: <bibl n="shak. rom 2.4.27" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. II, 4, 27</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>